txt.en: There are Stone-trolls encamped at the ruins of Barad Glamgil in Nan Tornaeth, in the Trollshaws.\n\nWhile in Nan Tornaeth, you should drive out the Stone-trolls which have settled there.
Stone-trolls have moved into Nan Tornaeth, settling in the ruins high above.
